  "text": "Universities have traditionally organized academic careers based on male life patterns, making it more difficult for women to advance their careers while building a family [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, the intensified organizational demands and current expectations from academics supposed to devote unlimited time to their work have raised new gender issues worth addressing.",
